body:
### We're making the move
The Next Jump blog is starting a migration.

We'll be porting over our old content form blog.nextjump.com (currently routed through tumblr) and eventually getting that domain to point here, so sit tight and enjoy the ride.

-NxJ Blog Team
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
